{"tid":2026634,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"戴祖儀「激凸」賣萌　網民錯重點：晾咗喺枱面","createTime":"2020-05-21T05:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T05:59:01.000Z","uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a10c21507f9bdd4b9e7ce2ca44a1d13bca2a23c","tid":2026634,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200521/photo/bkn-20200521084223427-0521_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200521092918\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200521%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200521084223427-0521_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200521092918&h=9d8c5bfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手戴祖儀（Joey）憑住長腿成功俘虜唔少宅男，但其實佢嘅上圍亦相當有料，好似早前佢喺社交網上載一張做瑜伽嘅獨照，雖然佢以手部半掩上半身，但都明顯睇到玲瓏浮凸嘅好身材，獲激讚「禾稈冚珍珠」！<br />\n今次佢再「加碼」派福利，上載一張自拍照，見佢嘴嘟嘟賣萌，相當可愛，不過重點係着上黑色緊身衫嘅佢靠近枱邊，「凸」顯出完美身段，即睇到一班網民嘩嘩聲，大讚佢認真「有料」，留言話「我係咪重點錯咗😂😂我只見到枱上嘅物體😍😍」、「晾起咗喺枱面」！"},{"pid":"596449e25675ad3e1935acc5fb6a8bba6425e8e2","tid":2026634,"uid":243075,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得呢條女好作狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0b3a0c595e6e56892c3206bd6cfe1202bac3d7","tid":2026634,"uid":208552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"究竟墊左幾多個pad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408fa62393a1f4830088916219cbcb011b303357","tid":2026634,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"596449e25675ad3e1935acc5fb6a8bba6425e8e2","tid":2026634,"uid":243075,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得呢條女好作狀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T05:44:00.000Z","msg":"over 左"},{"pid":"054be005df2f7b2e96bc3b499bdf4e580ef79af5","tid":2026634,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":